---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { absoluteUrl } from "../lib/site";

const canonicalUrl = absoluteUrl("/privacy-policy/");
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Visit Korea Planner"
  description="Privacy Policy for PlanMyKorea."
  bodyClass="page--leaf"
  canonicalUrl={canonicalUrl}
  alternateEnUrl={canonicalUrl}
  alternateEsUrl={canonicalUrl}
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>Last updated: February 2026</p>

    <p>
      PlanMyKorea ("we", "our", or "this website") is an informational website
      created to help international travelers find useful information when
      planning a trip to South Korea.
    </p>
    <p>
      We respect your privacy and are committed to being transparent about how
      data may be used on this site.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
    <p>We do not directly collect personal information from visitors.</p>
    <p>This means:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>No account registration</li>
      <li>No name or email collection</li>
      <li>No comments or user-submitted forms</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can browse this website anonymously.</p>

    <h2>2. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      Although we do not collect personal data ourselves, this website uses
      third-party services that may automatically collect limited information.
    </p>
    <p>These services include:</p>
    <p>These services include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Google AdSense (advertising)</li>
      <li>Google Analytics (traffic analysis)</li>
      <li>Microsoft Clarity (user behavior analytics)</li>
      <li>Cloudflare (website security and performance)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      These third parties may use cookies, web beacons, or similar
      technologies to collect non-personally identifiable information such as:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>IP address</li>
      <li>Browser type</li>
      <li>Device information</li>
      <li>Pages visited</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      This information is used to improve website performance and display
      relevant advertisements.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Cookies and Advertising</h2>
    <p>
      Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on
      users' visits to this and other websites.
    </p>
    <p>
      Users may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting:
      <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        https://adssettings.google.com
      </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      You can also learn more about how Google uses data from sites that use
      its services:
      <a
        href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads
      </a>
    </p>

    <h2>4. Purpose of This Website</h2>
    <p>
      All content on PlanMyKorea is provided for informational and travel
      guidance purposes only.
    </p>
    <p>
      We strive to keep information accurate and up to date, but we do not
      guarantee completeness or official accuracy. Travelers should always
      verify important details with official sources.
    </p>

    <h2>5. External Links</h2>
    <p>This website may contain links to external websites.</p>
    <p>
      We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of those
      third-party sites.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time.</p>
    <p>Any changes will be posted on this page.</p>

    <h2>7. Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you may contact us
      at:
    </p>
    <p>Email: bayernmc@gmail.com</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 10px 0 24px;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .legal-page h1 {
    margin: 0 0 20px;
  }

  .legal-page h2 {
    margin: 24px 0 8px;
  }

  .legal-page p {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
  }

  .legal-page ul {
    margin: 0 0 12px 20px;
    padding: 0;
  }
</style>
